description.en:
FnaticX Token will be used as a Payment for the Utility Services.
$FNAX Token will be used for utility services like D2h,mobile recharges,Paying Bills,Shopping,Buying Giftcards etc.And more utilities will be added,as these are the most important commodities currently in 21st century.
FnaticX will provide safe and secure Ecosystem payment gateway for Utility Services, where each and everyone can safely and securely transact through the FnaticX Token.
